"{\"uid\": \"dailytimes.com.pk-1226279-tom-cruises-paycheque-for-2024-olympics-stunt-revealed\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Daily Times  Your right to know  Published on:September 16, 2024 12:37 AM  It wasn't mission impossible for Tom Cruise to deliver the Olympic flag to Los Angeles after the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 108, \"end\": 118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 150, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.002993794725039e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But as it turns out, the Top Gun star agreed to pull off his dazzling death-defying stunt without receiving a paycheck.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We pitched on a Zoom,\\\" 2028 LA Olympics President and Chairperson Casey Wasserman said of the Closing Ceremony during a CNBC panel Sept. 11.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casey Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\"}, {\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999004103, \"rank\": 6.216934616747404e-11, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"About five minutes in the presentation, he goes, 'I am in.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am only doing it if I can do everything.'\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every step of the way, he got more involved and more engaged-and by the way, he did it all for free.\\\"\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"E!\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News has reached out to reps for Tom for comment but has not heard back.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a surprise for Casey and executive producer Ben Winston, who initially wanted to make the performance as easy as possible for Tom to take part.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Winston\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Winston\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Winston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Winston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The original idea was a person in the stadium as a stunt double,\\\" Casey recalled.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are like, 'Well, there is no way we are getting this.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to get four hours of filming time.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will do the thing in LA with the Hollywood sign, he will hand the thing off and he's done.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1121, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe we will get the other stuff and the rest will be just a stunt double.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Tom wanted to really be a part of the performance.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Ben could not help but gush over his commitment to the project.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think there is anybody like him in the world,\\\" he told The Hollywood Reporter last month.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0787698424631495e-37, \"text\": \"The Hollywood Reporter\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no better collaborator.\\\"\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, when the producer informed the Mission: Impossible actor that a stunt double would do the heavy lifting, he replied, \\\"We are not doing a stuntman in a balaclava.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to be the one who jumps off the roof, and I am going to be the one who drives through Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1785, \"end\": 1790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999967014901, \"rank\": 3.298443077539819e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for why they wanted Tom for the honor?\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not really think who else would work,\\\" Ben admitted to the outlet.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Who else is synonymous with action and an American hero?\\\"\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1953, \"end\": 1961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.998312886121056, \"rank\": 0.0016524829151689227, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 62-year-old's stunt that closed the chapter on this year's Olympic Games will surely go down in history.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Tom dove into the stadium, LA Mayor Karen Bass and Simone Biles presented him with the Olympic flag before he took it back to Los Angeles in true Mission: Impossible fashion.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karen Bass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\"}, {\"begin\": 2135, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 2210, \"end\": 2221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.002993794725039e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because for Tom, moving the goalpost for each project is crucial.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am always pushing,\\\" he told Business Insider last June.\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2356, \"end\": 2372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_Insider\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Business Insider\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_Insider\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_Insider\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just remember, every time they say, 'Can you top it?\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can you not top it?'\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"we are always pushing.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every film I do, whatever genre it's in, I want to make it as entertaining as possible for that audience.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I can do things better.\\\"\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Filed Under:Lifestyle          More Posts from this Category  More Posts from this Category  More Posts from this Category    HomeLead StoriesLatest NewsEditor's Picks  CultureLife & StyleFeaturedVideos  EditorialsOP-EDSCommentaryAdvertise  CartoonsLettersBlogsPrivacy Policy  ContactCompany's FinancialsInvestor InformationTerms & Conditions  FacebookTwitterInstagramYoutube  \\u00a9 2025 Daily Times.\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3040, \"entities\": []}]}"